#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/10.providers/05.registrar/ovh/manualdns.mdx:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "DNS Configuration with OVH"
msgstr "Настройка DNS с помощью OVH"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/10.providers/05.registrar/ovh/manualdns.mdx:7
#, no-wrap
msgid "Let's see how to properly set the DNS redirections with [OVH](http://www.ovh.com).\n"
msgstr ""
"Давайте посмотрим, как правильно настроить перенаправления DNS с помощью "
"[OVH](http://www.ovh.com).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/10.providers/05.registrar/ovh/manualdns.mdx:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "Once you bought your domain name, got to the Web Control Panel, and click on you domain name on the left side:\n"
msgstr ""
"После покупки доменного имени перейдите в панель управления и щёлкните по "
"своему доменному имени в левой части экрана:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/10.providers/05.registrar/ovh/manualdns.mdx:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "![OVH website screenshot](/img/providers/ovh_control_panel.png?resize=800)\n"
msgstr ""
"![Снимок экрана веб-сайта OVH]"
"(/img/providers/ovh_control_panel.png?resize=800)\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/10.providers/05.registrar/ovh/manualdns.mdx:13
#, no-wrap
msgid "Click on the **DNS Zone** tab, then on **Add an entry**:\n"
msgstr ""
"Перейдите на вкладку **DNS Zone**, затем нажмите **Add an entry "
"(Добавить запись)**:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/10.providers/05.registrar/ovh/manualdns.mdx:15
#, no-wrap
msgid "![OVH website screenshot](/img/providers/ovh_dns_zone.png?resize=800)\n"
msgstr ""
"![Снимок экрана веб-сайта OVH](/img/providers/ovh_dns_zone.png?resize=800)\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/10.providers/05.registrar/ovh/manualdns.mdx:17
#, no-wrap
msgid "Now you need to add the DNS redirections as specified by the [standard DNS zone configuration](/admin/get_started/post_install/dns_config)\n"
msgstr ""
"Теперь необходимо добавить перенаправления DNS в соответствии со "
"[стандартной конфигурацией зоны DNS]"
"(/admin/get_started/post_install/dns_config)\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/10.providers/05.registrar/ovh/manualdns.mdx:19
#, no-wrap
msgid "Click on \"Change in text format\", keep the first four lines:\n"
msgstr ""
"Нажмите на кнопку «Изменить формат текста», оставив первые четыре строки:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/10.providers/05.registrar/ovh/manualdns.mdx:28
#, no-wrap
msgid "then erase everything below, and replace it with the configuration generated by YunoHost as explained in [this page](/admin/get_started/post_install/dns_config).\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/10.providers/05.registrar/ovh/manualdns.mdx:29
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/40.post_install/20.dns_config.mdx:93
#, no-wrap
msgid "Dynamic IP"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/10.providers/05.registrar/ovh/manualdns.mdx:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "[General tutorial on dynamic IP](/admin/tutorials/domains/dns_dynamicip).\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/10.providers/05.registrar/ovh/manualdns.mdx:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "You should follow this part if you have a dynamic IP.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/10.providers/05.registrar/ovh/manualdns.mdx:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "Find out if your ISP provides you with a dynamic IP address [here](/admin/get_started/providers/isp/).\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/10.providers/05.registrar/ovh/manualdns.mdx:38
#, no-wrap
msgid "Let's create a DynHost id.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/10.providers/05.registrar/ovh/manualdns.mdx:41
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Follow [this tutorial](http://blog.developpez.com/brutus/p6316/ubuntu/configurer_dynhost_ovh_avec_ddclient) to install ddclient.\n"
"ddclient will take care of telling OVH that the IP has changed. Then OVH will update the IP.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/10.providers/05.registrar/ovh/manualdns.mdx:43
#, no-wrap
msgid "You need to add in the configuration file:\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/10.providers/05.registrar/ovh/manualdns.mdx:46
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"- your login and password DynHost\n"
"- your domain name\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/10.providers/05.registrar/ovh/manualdns.mdx:47
#, no-wrap
msgid "You should also check out [OVH's guide on DynHost](https://www.ovh.co.uk/g2024.hosting_dynhost).\n"
msgstr ""
